      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Anticipating ChatGPT 5: Unveiling Insights into OpenAI's Next Chatbot</h5>
        <p class="card-text">The impending release of ChatGPT 5 has stirred excitement and curiosity within the tech community, as enthusiasts eagerly</p>
        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">More</a> -->
        <form action="/top-blog-1" method="GET">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">More</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card example-blog" style="width: 18rem;">
      <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4E12AQH5R42BmXx17A/article-cover_image-shrink_720_1280/0/1694967432251?e=1715817600&v=beta&t=QxfSRduML12hdmQT7393ySmc-piVFwIivRH5-D29ql4" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">The Advantages of Freelancing: A Path to Flexibility and Autonomy</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Freelancing has emerged as a dynamic and liberating career choice, offering a plethora of advantages that extend beyond the</p>
        <form action="/top-blog-2" method="GET">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">More</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card example-blog" style="width: 18rem;">
      <img src="images/pizza-blog.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="pizza">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Homemade Pizzas: A Scrumptious Symphony of Health and Flavor</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Embarking on the journey of crafting homemade pizzas not only promises a palate-pleasing experience but also opens the door</p>
        <form action="/top-blog-3" method="GET">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">More</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include("./partials/footer.ejs") %>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="script/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>